{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">a blank slate is the best slate</span>", "lines": ["TITLE: The Legend of Fangs: Scene 2", "Narrator: Fangs and Peony embark down a quiet forest trail. Snoozletown looms dimly in the distance?", "Fangs: So, can you tell me more about these Snoozlestones? What even are they?&nbsp;", "PEONY: Legend, has it that they are the creation of genius, and the result of a bitter fight between two royal brothers.", "FANGS: This is how these kind of tales always begin.", "PEONY: The struggle for power is often the invisible hand behind many creations, what else can be said?", "PEONY: Anyways, legend has it that many centuries ago, a younger brother was left enraged when his elder inherited the throne of their father, who was the Duke of Snoozletown.&nbsp;", "PEONY: Seeking the throne, but well versed in the Machiavellian arts, the brother left Snoozletown, posing as an envoy, secretly seeking out a secret cult known for their practice of the mystic arts.", "NARRATOR: Fangs begins to wonder if all this hassle is really worth it. The mouse continues...", "PEONY: Using coin stolen from the royal bank, the younger brother purchased the recipe for a magical potion produced by the cult know as melatonitze. Even a small dosage could induce an prolonged slumber.&nbsp;&nbsp;", "PEONY: Knowing that killing his brother would implicate himself as the main suspect, the brother instead used melatonitze to synthesize the very first \"Snoozlestone\".", "FANGS: And did it work?", "PEONY: It did indeed, the younger brother slipped the Snoozlestone into his brother's dessert one morning, and the next morning the Duke did not awaken.", "Narrator: A faint hum of activity is now audible as Fangs and Peony near Snoozletown.&nbsp;", "PEONY: The younger brother was estatic. With his brother effectively in a coma, he would rule in his brother's stead temporarily. The power was his, while the crime remained anonymous.", "PEONY: But the dosage had been much too strong, and as decades passed and the brother's slumber continued, a guilt began to eat away at the mind of the younger brother...insomnia ensued.", "PEONY: Seeking respite and rest, the younger brother reformulated his original Snoozlestone recipe, diluting the melatonizte to a fraction of its former amount, and producing the a new Snoozlestone designed to only last a night without the coma inducing effects of the first Snoozlestone. Thus the the modern Snoozlestone was born. They exist, but a an exclusive commodity in Snoozletown.", "FANGS: Wait, that's it? The younger brother just got away with his crime, the end?", "PEONY: What did you expect, the world is a brutal place. Anyways there is not more time to digress. Snoozletown approaches, you human English is awful and moral orgins aside, Snoozlestones are suitable for your current predicament.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Fair enough, I need not concern myself with the follies of humans. I...", "PEONY: (whisper) Shh.. Something is coming.", "NARRATOR: Noises emmenate from the forest ahead.", "NARRATOR: Fangs insides knotted. He wished he had just eaten this foolish mouse.", "PEONY: (whisper) I know another way into Snoozletown, we'll have to go through the sewers.", "SCENE: End of scene 2."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Joanna", "TITLE": "Joanna", "Narrator": "Joanna", "Fangs": "Joanna", "PEONY": "Joanna", "FANGS": "Joanna", "SCENE": "Joanna"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "096168c44ae4187aac84f68c386963d6", "audio_objects": [["510066965c9f0901c4a3127dd50da638-the-legend-of-fangs--scen---", 0], ["209d47e2a1051e4ecd79a362116c81d6-narrator--fangs-and-peony---", 0], ["d8105995da01ce815e92c5abe6480c63-fangs--so--can-you-tell-m---", 0], ["c3b896fc7e79e2d7154210d61e76c397-legend--has-it-that-they----", 0], ["9ccacb2bf51a554c80ae824d47b70c20-this-is-how-these-kind-of---", 0], ["468303552df87122a3b9884f2913d84e-the-struggle-for-power-is---", 0], ["a5b81e659ed2b23eca5132dd952354a8-anyways--legend-has-it-th---", 0],